      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Smart Set</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I am 15 and I spend much of my free time researching cliques and stereotypes in junior high and high school. The teenagers in your article are only one type of nerd -- the lucky ones, blessed with friends, social skills and opportunity. Not all nerds are like that. We do not always have someone to turn to, something to do or someone to help us.</p>
        <p>Eve Garrick</p>
        <p>Orange, Conn.</p>
      </block>
